# QUEUE — approved slate cuts to build

`run next` pops the top **unchecked** row, builds it (per `../SLATE-RUNNER.md`),
then checks it off and records the review-MP4 path. Full candidate cards live in
the book's scout file — read the numbered card there for hook, exclusions, and
manim move before building.

Reels build into the book's own `youtube/<slug>/` (co-located with the book),
not into this toolkit. Done-links below point at the current `unreal-reels/reels/`
locations (pre-migration).

